Python program to display the largest factor of a positive number entered by the user.

number=int(input("Enter a positive number:"))
if number<=0:
    print("Please enter a positive number.")
else:
    for i in range(number-1, 0 ,-1):
        if number%i==0:
            largest=i
            break
print(f"The largest factor of {number} (other than itself) is: {largest} ")
